# ============================================================
# Application Branding
# ============================================================
# Displayed in the header, footer, login page, and browser title.
NUXT_PUBLIC_APP_NAME=Event Management System
NUXT_PUBLIC_COMPANY_NAME=Friendship Community

# ============================================================
# Supabase
# ============================================================
# Get these from your Supabase project dashboard:
# https://app.supabase.com/project/_/settings/api
#
# SUPABASE_URL        – The API URL of your Supabase project
# SUPABASE_ANON_KEY   – The public anonymous (anon) key
NUXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=
NUXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=

# ============================================================
# Default Event Cover Image
# ============================================================
# URL placeholder untuk event yang belum punya cover image (upload optional).
# Dipakai oleh helper `resolveEventImage()` di utils/event-image.ts
# sehingga halaman publik (home, detail) dan dashboard (events table,
# master user detail) tidak pernah render <img> kosong / broken.
#
# Bisa di-host di mana saja yang reachable oleh browser:
#   - Supabase Storage public bucket (recommended)
#   - CDN (Cloudflare, Imgix, dsb.)
#   - Path absolut ke file di folder public/ (otomatis di-serve Nuxt)
#   - URL HTTPS external (Unsplash, dsb.)
#
# Kalau dikosongkan, kartu / halaman detail akan menampilkan icon
# placeholder (`<i class="fa-regular fa-image">`) instead of an <img>.
NUXT_PUBLIC_DEFAULT_EVENT_IMAGE=
